{"tid":1357014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[NOW即日焦點] 721警方上環驅散示威者未有示警橋上開槍","createTime":"2019-07-23T15:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T08:54:17.000Z","uid":94771,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"9523fd8002601a80d0872edb5dc835a2e87ab0c3","tid":1357014,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2019-07-23-22-08-09fiW7Prze.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2019-07-23-22-08-09fiW7Prze.jpg&h=e030742a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E-fSYVGc02I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE-fSYVGc02I&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=d819a918\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E-fSYVGc02I</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】星期日反修例遊行後，大批示威者集結在上環，警方施放催淚彈及發射橡膠子彈驅散。醫管局指，有十四人受傷，目前仍有一人留醫，情況穩定。本台發現，警方在未有示警下，在橋上向橋下示威者開槍，有人權組織批評做法不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n大批示威者星期日晚在上環集結，警方九時半展開驅散行動。<br />\n<br />\n本台獲得一條影片，拍攝到當晚在中區警署外行人天橋有速龍小隊監察橋下情況，期間警員驅趕記者，在無任何警告下，向橋下的示威者發射橡膠子彈，橋上留下彈殼。幾分鐘後，再有警員在未有示警下發射胡椒球彈。<br />\n<br />\n人權監察當晚有派員留意有關情況，認為警員在橋上開槍兼且未有示警，做法不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後出示黑旗，多次施放催淚彈驅散示威者，亦向示威者連開多槍，包括胡椒球彈和布袋彈。<br />\n<br />\n多人吸入催淚氣體不適，亦有記者懷疑被橡膠子彈打中受傷。<br />\n<br />\n羅沃啟認為，相較612金鐘衝突，當晚警方使用武力，仍無改善亦不恰當。他又說，當晚發現有很多警員身上沒有佩戴委任證或警員編號，重申應成立獨立調查委員會調查這些情況。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆指，警務人員在使用武力前會在情況許可下，向對方發出警告，任何人如認為警方處事時受不合理對待，可向投訴警察課投訴。<br />\n<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356445&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=38c9ae3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356445&h=897e79f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356445</a>"},{"pid":"4fbf775a564aec1952bdd08e760ddc0723b4d330","tid":1357014,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:42:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dda4009c9217bef8dbd77cb1acd772c4150ab1c","tid":1357014,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:42:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f63f046c644438bf829678f66b681114a2c0fb77","tid":1357014,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"咁撚痴線"},{"pid":"a1f0a08dd69c5f8f96a0e595793edda81c48c2ac","tid":1357014,"uid":269695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df5b6f1b2f069e1d9e281523826d13a571989180","tid":1357014,"uid":59039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:44:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d4113546db4af4888265f45626cb5616a858de12","tid":1357014,"uid":104247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:44:51.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7be3180534d14f21f1e3310d1bdda89d5a2b98","tid":1357014,"uid":156611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad9b0729c52f365930bc535c8f9c776f058a82a6","tid":1357014,"uid":15719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5d53e8ae152ad6f5ac56152ff60584f6a6c9f8b","tid":1357014,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"成晚都好鬼<br />\n<br />\n係咪射爆頭玩大左<br />\n<br />\n到依家都冇公報幾多人俾警察打傷送院<br />\n<br />\n射左幾多槍冇講<br />\n<br />\ntear gas 射幾多又冇講"